Package: translateVTT
Type: Package
Title: Automatically translate VTT files
Version: 1.0.3
Author: Vladimir Zhbanko
Maintainer: Vladimir Zhbanko <vladimir.zhbanko@gmail.com>
Description: Facilitate automated translation of files with a complex structure.
    Imports user files from a specified directory. Extracts text with closed captions.
    Sends this text to Google Translate API and retrieves back the translation.
    Original file structure will be restored. Provides facility to encrypt API keys.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    readr,
    openssl,
    translateR (>= 1.0),
    utils
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://vladdsm.github.io/myblog_attempt/topics/topics-AutotranslateGoogleAPI.html
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
